//Events
(click),only if left side of mouse is clicked
(mouseover)
mousedown , if any mouse button is clicked.
mouseup, once you leave the click the event is fired.
dblclicl , double click
drag, drag the element.
drag over , everytime the held element is dragged over something. 

keydown , everythime you type.
keyup , when you release a key.
focus , when you click on the inout field.

